            . I am an officer. I apprehended the prisoner, and found a shirt on his back - I have known him ten years; he has borne a very good character.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He owed me a trifle; I went to ask him for it, and he said he could not pay - I thought the shirts worth about what he owed me, and I took them.</p>
